com.interpss.core.aclf.netAdj

Interface AclfNetAdjustment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.hazelcast.nio.serialization.DataSerializable, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, NameTag, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AclfNetAdjustmentImpl

    public interface AclfNetAdjustment
extends NameTag
    A representation of the model object 'Aclf Net Adjustment'. Container for those adjustment elements which could be only at the Aclf network level, instead of AclfBus or Aclfbranch level.

    The following features are supported:

    • Aclf Net
    • Area Interchange Control List
    • Interarea Transfer List
    • Tie Line Interfaces
    See Also:
    NetAdjustPackage.getAclfNetAdjustment()
